    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What is TypeScript Setup?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Setting up TypeScript involves installing the compiler, configuring project settings, and compiling TypeScript code into JavaScript."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Install TypeScript"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "npm install -g typescript"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Check Version"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "tsc -v"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Initialize Project"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "tsc --init"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "tsconfig.json Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "json",
      "value": "{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"target\": \"ES6\",\n    \"module\": \"commonjs\",\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\"\n  }\n}"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Compile TypeScript"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "tsc app.ts"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Watch Mode"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "tsc --watch"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Project Structure"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "text",
      "value": "project/\n├── src/\n│   └── app.ts\n├── dist/\n├── tsconfig.json\n└── package.json"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use tsconfig.json for configuration**",
